{"tid":2284743,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"新iPhone炒唔起12 Pro 僅賺千元 料今現放售潮 隨時蝕讓","createTime":"2020-11-13T14:12:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T14:12:59.000Z","uid":13745,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8349d71de6be3d2c81103f45798f70063e6e58de","tid":2284743,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T14:12:59.000Z","msg":"iPhone 12及iPhone 12 Pro 昨於武肺疫情嚴峻下開售，外界於開售前早已吹淡風。先達昨午曾出現收機價「小陽春」，iPhone 12 Pro太平洋藍512GB收機價一度炒至12,800元，較原價高1,801元，惟iPhone 12 128GB僅微賺1元，晚上更是後勁不繼，12 Pro 太平洋藍512GB跌至不足1,000元水位，普通版更即日「炒燶」。市場料今日更多人會放售，令炒價再跌。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201024/QNNZNSRTVBDD3FICG7FMT65FZY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201024%2FQNNZNSRTVBDD3FICG7FMT65FZY%2F&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIs5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=209fe2e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201024%2FQNNZNSRTVBDD3FICG7FMT65FZY%2F&h=d977f25d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201024/QNNZNSRTVBDD3FICG7FMT65FZY/</a>"}]}